function ISRADIUS = IsRadius(windowPtrOrScreenNumber)% ISRADIUS = IsRadius(windowPtrOrScreenNumber)%% Obsolete.  Use IsRadius10 instead.% % Reads driver name to determine whether the% card is a Radius 10-bit card.  This is useful% to determine how to write the CLUT ('SetClut'% or 'Gamma').%% The answer is cached the first time this is% called, so that subsequent calls are fast.% 2/27/02  dhb,ly  Made obsolete.ISRADIUS = IsRadius10(windowPtrOrScreenNumber);